      <div class="why-block">
        <h1 class="why">Why ?</h1>

        <div class="tripple-wrapper">
          
          <div class="tripple-card">
          <i class="fas fa-balance-scale"></i>
          <p class="title-card">Honest feedback</p>
          <p>It's anonymous.
          People are not afraid anymore
          to say what they think.
          They will provide an honest 
          and qualitative feedback.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="tripple-card">
          <i class="fas fa-lock-open"></i>
          <p class="title-card">Think broader</p>
          <p>Discover different ways of thinking you didn't think about. <br>
          It will give you a wider aspect of your speech and that will help you to improve your way to pitch.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="tripple-card">
          <i class="fas fa-history"></i>
          <p class="title-card">Time-saving</p>
          <p>With my:rror, creating your form is quick and easy, thanks to some predefined questions. Everything is thought to save you time.</p>
          </div>
        
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="quote-container">
        <div class="quote">
        “We all need people who will give us feedback. That's how we improve.”<br>
        </div>
        
